An arcade game that will keep you busy for a while.

Your goal is to clear all the bubbles from the board, scoring as many points as possible. Just shoot at them with the bubbles that appear at bottom - point your mouse to where you want the next bubble to go, and click to fire the shot, When three or more bubbles of the same color come together, they all explode.

The more bubbles blow up at one shot, the better for your score. Take into account that ten bubbles at one shot is better than two shots of five. Besides, those bubbles that fell apart from the rest will explode too. It is well worth trying to arrange such avalanches, as they will give you ten times more points than ordinary bursts.

The string of bubbles at the left corner shows how many misses (shots without explosions) are left until new bubbles will pop up. If you manage to blow up all the bubbles of some color, they will not appear later in the game. At this moment you get a bonus, and new bubbles too, to balance it. The few colors are left in play, the more lines will be added after every miss.
The game ends when you clean all the bubbles off or they move all the way                      down on you.
The following features are present in registered version:
* games can be saved in the middle, and later restored
* you can auto-save all the current setup settings
* the Help window does not bother you any more
* the best scores table is saved to disk
* you can pick a skill level of the game
